        &lt;p&gt;Radius Applications are able to connect to and leverage Kubernetes resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;resource-library&#34;&gt;Resource library&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Visit &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Azure/bicep-types-k8s/blob/main/generated/index.md&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; to reference the Kubernetes resource.&lt;/p&gt;









